Privacy Policy
Effective Date: [26/12/2024]

This Privacy Policy explains how Hedieaty collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you use our mobile application ("the App"). By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

1. Information We Collect
When you register for an account on the App, we collect the following personal information:

Name: Your full name, which is used to personalize your experience.
Email Address: Your email address, which is used for authentication and communication purposes (e.g., password recovery).
2. How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information for the following purposes:

Account Creation: To create and manage your account on the App.
Authentication: To verify your identity and allow access to your account.
Communication: To send you important updates, notifications, and account-related messages.
3. Data Storage and Protection
We store your personal information securely using industry-standard practices. The data you provide is stored on secure servers with appropriate safeguards to protect it from unauthorized access.

We do not share your personal information with third parties, except where necessary to provide the services, such as authentication services via Firebase.

4. Data Retention
We will retain your personal information for as long as necessary to provide the services you request or as required by law.

5. Your Rights
You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. If you wish to delete your account or update your information, you can contact us at 21P0334@eng.asu.edu.eg

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will post the updated policy on this page and update the "Effective Date" at the top of the page. We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any changes.

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: 21P0334@eng.asu.edu.eg
